        "recipient_id": "9c1ec395-7a2e-ac81-70e3-371cfa83f023-C",
        "award_amount": 1166618.83,
        "description": "In its extended mission  twins will continue to visualize 3d global ion dynamics  composition  origins and destinies. Twins observations over the next 5 years of the solar cycle are crucial to capture the systems-level view of geospace for the full range of geomagnetic and solar activity conditions and provide the only available global magnetospheric context imaging for the in situ magnetospheric observations in the heliospheric system observatory.",
